entries.s_11: Huh. That ... I think I'm feeling a bit better.
entries.s_13: Rest here for a bit, then go drink lots of fluids.
entries.s_15: Thank you! I shouldn't say this, but I have friends in the Alliance. If you want to do some work for them, talk to Droma Ordo in Anchorhead. You will have to find him, but he will make it worth your while.
entries.s_20: Have you been able to stand?
entries.s_22: No, not at all. The world is spinning and I feel sick.
entries.s_28: Oh.. I can't... see too well. Everything is spinning.
entries.s_8: Ok. I think I can take care of it. Be very still.
entries.s_9: I'm going to take some time rest until I feel better.
